===Prefix===
{{infl|en|prefix|cat=prefixes}}

# As an [[intensifier]]; i.e. [[thoroughly]], [[excessively]]
# [[on|On]], [[around]], [[over]] or in [[contact]] with something.
# [[verb|Verbs]] derived from [[nouns]] (e.g. befriend,
behead, benight), or from [[adjectives]] (e.g. bedim, bewet).

